print("Nhập kéo, búa, bao")

player=input()
computer = randint(0,2)
if computer == 0:
computer = "Đấm"
if computer == 1:
computer = "Kéo"
if computer == 2:
computer = "Bao"
print(computer)
if player == computer:
print("Draw")
else:
if player == "Kéo":
if computer == "Đấm":
print("Lose")
if computer == "Bao":
print("Win")
if player == "Đấm":
if computer == "Bao":
print("Lose")
if computer == "Kéo":
print("Win")
if player == "Bao":
if computer == "Kéo":
print("Lose")
if computer == "Đấm":
print("Win")
